						<summary>

						<p>This inscription which is much damaged refers to the reign of king <hi rend="bold">[Iṟiva]beḍaṅgadēva,</hi> who is stated to have been ruling over the <hi rend="bold">Eḍadoṟe country.</hi> His minister <hi rend="italic">(perggaḍe)</hi> <hi rend="bold">Chandima[yya]</hi> and (the gods ?) Ādityadēva and another are mentioned as donees. The date is lost.</p>						

						</summary>
